## Project Overview

Memory is an Android application designed to provide personalized cognitive training instead of a traditional memory game.

Rather than relying on predefined difficulty levels, the application continuously analyses player behaviour, identifies cognitive patterns and dynamically adapts future gameplay to the user's performance.

The project was independently designed, implemented and documented in less than one month using an AI-assisted development workflow.

